    {
      "id": "PopularPost232612",
      "post_content": "Recoil.  \n  \nHow you made me cry when you first came out.  \nHow many times did you turn into [vindicate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=vindicate), with added insult from [megrim](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=megrim)?  \n  \nAfter planar chaos came out, a friend of mine had a strange UBR control deck. His favourite thing to do was to recoil his [flametongue kavu](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=flametongue kavu), and discard into [reckless wurm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=reckless wurm), with madness. Bizarre, but strangely effective.  \n  \nStill one of my favourite bounce spells (along with the aptly named [snap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=snap));  \n4.5/5   \n  \n*And* it's a common!",
      "posted_by": "Sharu",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost232612\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Recoil.<br/><br/>How you made me cry when you first came out.<br/>How many times did you turn into <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"vindicate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=vindicate\">vindicate</a>, with added insult from <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"megrim\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=megrim\">megrim</a>?<br/><br/>After planar chaos came out, a friend of mine had a strange UBR control deck. His favourite thing to do was to recoil his <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"flametongue kavu\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=flametongue kavu\">flametongue kavu</a>, and discard into <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"reckless wurm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=reckless wurm\">reckless wurm</a>, with madness. Bizarre, but strangely effective.<br/><br/>Still one of my favourite bounce spells (along with the aptly named <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"snap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=snap\">snap</a>);<br/>4.5/5 <br/><br/><i>And</i> it's a common!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '232612'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80001\">Sharu</span>\r\n            